  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Using mobile smartphones to monitor gibbons (Hylobatidae) and poaching in Vietnam</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In this project, the aim is to use mobile smartphones to monitor gunshots and gibbon populations in several protected areas (PA) of Vietnam. Project objectives are as follows: (1) To apply mobile smartphones to survey and monitor gibbon populations; (2) To apply mobile smartphones to monitor hunting activities in selected PAs; and (3) To train the protected area staff and rangers to use mobile smartphones in monitoring wildlife populations and hunting activities.</narrative>
  </description>
